		<description><![CDATA[Last week we talked with a few of Corona's Core Engineers and explored the mechanics of two tough steering, all live from the Palo Alto office and just days before GDC16.]]></description>
				<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><iframe width="800" height="450" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JmqJj7qdEAE?rel=0&amp;showinfo=0" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p>
<p><img class="alignright wp-image-477" src="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/corona-geek-head-transparent-150x150.png" alt="Corona Geek" width="105" height="105" srcset="/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/corona-geek-head-transparent-150x150.png 150w, /wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/corona-geek-head-transparent.png 250w" sizes="(max-width: 105px) 100vw, 105px" />Last week we recorded the Corona Geek podcast live from the Palo Alto office ahead of a week filled with <a href=https://www.facebook.com/CoronaGeek/photos target="_blank">GDC Expo awesomeness</a>. We talked with a few of Corona&#8217;s Core Engineers and explored the mechanics of two tough steering. As you can see, we had a pretty good time together and it was a unique opportunity to hang with the Corona team and hear them talk about the topics you care about.</p>
<p>Download the <a href=http://github.com/roaminggamer/CoronaGeek/raw/master/Hangouts/Tips_and_Tricks/two_touch_steering.zip target="_blank">two touch steering demo source code</a>.</p>
